docs/WEEKLY_PLANNING_GUIDE.md

# Secret-leak incidents log (#634) — append-only metadata om hook-detections.
# Indeholder type-navne + 8-char prefix/4-char suffix previews; ikke ægte secrets,
# men forsigtig: keep local.
.claude/secret-leak-incidents.log

# Secret-leak stats log (forward-guard for #634 screenshot false-positive).
# Append-only image-mode + leak telemetry. Local-only — same pattern as
# secret-leak-incidents.log above. Gitleaks allowlist eksisterer som
# defensiv backup hvis logfilen alligevel ender staged.
.claude/secret-leak-stats.log

# Playwright MCP tool artifacts (browser-nav snapshots/logs)
.playwright-mcp/
.superpowers/

# Local DB backup artifacts (scripts/db-backup.mjs default output). Real prod
# backups must NEVER be committed — point BACKUP_DIR at OneDrive for off-site.
/.backups/
